{
  "id": "6a205d3e955577ad150d28d4",
  "title": "井戸端荘:「一緒にメシ食う」しに来ました",
  "created": 1780505928,
  "updated": 1780509347,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a205d3e955577ad150d28d4",
      "text": "井戸端荘:「一緒にメシ食う」しに来ました",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780505928,
      "updated": 1780505928
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205d4700000000008fe7c6",
      "text": "前回: [井戸端荘: お近づきホモサピエンス]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780505928,
      "updated": 1780505933
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205d4900000000008fe7c7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780505929,
      "updated": 1780505929
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205d4f00000000008fe7c8",
      "text": "[*** プロローグ — 既に居る]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780505935,
      "updated": 1780506140
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e1800000000008fe7c9",
      "text": "夕方。inajob がリビングに入ると、ソファの真ん中に 青い長髪の猫耳少女が既に座っていた。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506136,
      "updated": 1780506136
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e3800000000008fe7e4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506168,
      "updated": 1780506168
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e1800000000008fe7ca",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]「あれ」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506136,
      "updated": 1780506136
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e1800000000008fe7cb",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「[やあ、観察対象のホモ・サピエンスのみなさん]」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506136,
      "updated": 1780507400
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e1800000000008fe7cc",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「『[一緒にメシ食う]』をしに来ました」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506136,
      "updated": 1780506173
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e1800000000008fe7cd",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]「(本気で来た)」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506136,
      "updated": 1780506136
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e1800000000008fe7ce",
      "text": "[takker.icon]「ホワイトボードに予告がないのが今回の特徴」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506136,
      "updated": 1780506136
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e3f00000000008fe7e5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506176,
      "updated": 1780506176
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e1800000000008fe7cf",
      "text": "冷蔵庫のホワイトボードを見ると、クオリアさん専用枠には特に何も書かれていない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506136,
      "updated": 1780506176
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e4100000000008fe7e6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506177,
      "updated": 1780506177
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e1800000000008fe7d0",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「観察対象に予告を行うと観察精度が低下します。我々の通常運用では、観察対象には予告しません」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506136,
      "updated": 1780506177
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e1800000000008fe7d1",
      "text": "[caki.icon]「いきなり来たほうが自然な姿が見られるから、ってこと?」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506136,
      "updated": 1780506136
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e1800000000008fe7d2",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「あなた方の語彙では、そう翻訳されます」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506136,
      "updated": 1780506136
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e1800000000008fe7d3",
      "text": "[mtane0412.icon]「翻訳構文がうつる」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506136,
      "updated": 1780506136
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e1800000000008fe7d4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506136,
      "updated": 1780506136
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e1800000000008fe7d5",
      "text": "[*** 1. メニュー]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506136,
      "updated": 1780506164
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e2f00000000008fe7d6",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]「で、何食べる」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506160,
      "updated": 1780506160
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e2f00000000008fe7d7",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「プリンを持ってきました」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506160,
      "updated": 1780506160
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e4600000000008fe7e7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506182,
      "updated": 1780506182
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e2f00000000008fe7d8",
      "text": "クオリアさんの手元に、いつの間にか皿に乗ったプリンがあった。プリン本体は普通の色をしているが、上にかかった ソースが[青く発光している]。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506160,
      "updated": 1780506190
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e4700000000008fe7e8",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/1f6a48d421974a3609d48b5e6e179855]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506184,
      "updated": 1780509347
    },
    {
      "id": "6a206aa300000000008fe8fd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780509347,
      "updated": 1780509347
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e2f00000000008fe7d9",
      "text": "[takker.icon]「プリン、と言いつつソースが青い」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506160,
      "updated": 1780506184
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e2f00000000008fe7da",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]「(発光しているプリン)」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506160,
      "updated": 1780506160
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e2f00000000008fe7db",
      "text": "[terang.icon]「[それはチェレンコフ光ではないのか]」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506160,
      "updated": 1780506197
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e2f00000000008fe7dc",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「観察対象の標準的な食事カテゴリから一品を持参しました。プリン本体は標準仕様です。ソースは我々の通常運用における正常形態です」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506160,
      "updated": 1780506160
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e2f00000000008fe7dd",
      "text": "[blu3mo.icon]「(波長を測定したい)」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506160,
      "updated": 1780506160
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e2f00000000008fe7de",
      "text": "[caki.icon]「食べていいやつなんですか……?」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506160,
      "updated": 1780506160
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e2f00000000008fe7df",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「観察対象による摂取は、観察対象の自己観測量を増加させます。摂取可能性は観察対象の判断に委ねられます」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506160,
      "updated": 1780506160
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e2f00000000008fe7e0",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]「クオリアさんが判断を投げてきた」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506160,
      "updated": 1780506160
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e2f00000000008fe7e1",
      "text": "[takker.icon]「とりあえずプリンは保留で、メイン考えるから台所いくわ」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506160,
      "updated": 1780506160
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e6000000000008fe7e9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506208,
      "updated": 1780506208
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e2f00000000008fe7e2",
      "text": "inajob と takker が台所に向かう。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506160,
      "updated": 1780506208
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e2f00000000008fe7e3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506160,
      "updated": 1780506160
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e6000000000008fe7ea",
      "text": "[*** 2. sta が切り出す]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506209,
      "updated": 1780506235
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e7500000000008fe800",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506230,
      "updated": 1780506230
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e7500000000008fe801",
      "text": "リビングに残った sta は、ソファに座る QS を遠巻きに見ている。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506230,
      "updated": 1780506230
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e7500000000008fe802",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506230,
      "updated": 1780506230
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e7500000000008fe803",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「(……)」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506230,
      "updated": 1780506230
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e7500000000008fe805",
      "text": "[caki.icon]「sta、なんか動揺してない?」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506230,
      "updated": 1780506230
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e7500000000008fe807",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]「動揺の振り付けが本物」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506230,
      "updated": 1780506230
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e7500000000008fe809",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「いや、ちょっと、聞きたいことがあって」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506230,
      "updated": 1780506230
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e7500000000008fe80b",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「クオリアさん」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506230,
      "updated": 1780506230
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e7500000000008fe80d",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「どうぞ」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506230,
      "updated": 1780506230
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e7500000000008fe80f",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「俺、最近、井戸端で『[会社でみんなで食欲を満たすイベント]は頭おかしい』って書いたじゃないですか」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506230,
      "updated": 1780507781
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e7500000000008fe811",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「観察しました」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506230,
      "updated": 1780506230
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e7500000000008fe813",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]「(やっぱり)」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506230,
      "updated": 1780506230
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e7500000000008fe814",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506230,
      "updated": 1780506246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e8600000000008fe817",
      "text": "[*** 3. 同型に気づく]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506246,
      "updated": 1780506258
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e8d00000000008fe818",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506254,
      "updated": 1780506254
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e8d00000000008fe819",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「で、今、クオリアさんに『一緒にメシ食う』しに来られて、気づいたんですけど」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506254,
      "updated": 1780506254
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e8d00000000008fe81b",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「井戸端荘でみんなで一緒にメシを食うのは、井戸端荘でみんなで食欲を満たすイベントなのでは?」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506254,
      "updated": 1780506254
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e8d00000000008fe81d",
      "text": "[mtane0412.icon]「同型」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506254,
      "updated": 1780506254
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e8d00000000008fe81f",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「俺は、頭がおかしいことになる」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506254,
      "updated": 1780506254
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e8d00000000008fe821",
      "text": "[takker.icon]「それ自滅やん」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506254,
      "updated": 1780506254
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e8d00000000008fe823",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「観察された事実: 観察対象 sta の発話には、二つの異なる事実観察が含まれています。両者の整合性を整理します」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506254,
      "updated": 1780506254
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e8d00000000008fe824",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506254,
      "updated": 1780506254
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205e9f00000000008fe825",
      "text": "[*** 4. 規範は逆]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506272,
      "updated": 1780506287
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205eaf00000000008fe830",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506288,
      "updated": 1780506288
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205ea900000000008fe826",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「あなた方の文明では、食欲は公的に晒され、性欲は私的に隠されます」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506282,
      "updated": 1780506288
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205ea900000000008fe827",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「機能から見ると、食欲は個体維持のための私的欲求、性欲は種の維持のための公益的欲求です。現状の規範は逆です」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506282,
      "updated": 1780506282
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205ea900000000008fe828",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]「(これ前にも聞いた気がする)」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506282,
      "updated": 1780506282
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205ea900000000008fe829",
      "text": "[takker.icon]「[クオリアさん day 15] で言ってたやつ」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506282,
      "updated": 1780506299
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205ea900000000008fe82a",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「観察された事実: 観察対象 sta の井戸端での主張は、我々の機能論的整理と一致しています」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506282,
      "updated": 1780506282
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205ea900000000008fe82b",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「俺、知らないうちにクオリアさんの Day 15 をなぞってたのか」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506282,
      "updated": 1780506282
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205ea900000000008fe82c",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「観察された事実です」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506282,
      "updated": 1780506282
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205ea900000000008fe82d",
      "text": "[caki.icon]「sta、無自覚に賢かったらしい」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506282,
      "updated": 1780506282
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205ea900000000008fe82e",
      "text": "[mtane0412.icon]「これで終わるはずがない」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506282,
      "updated": 1780506282
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205ea900000000008fe82f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506282,
      "updated": 1780506282
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205ed000000000008fe831",
      "text": "[*** 5. 性欲は情報共有欲]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506321,
      "updated": 1780506334
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205ee300000000008fe83d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506340,
      "updated": 1780506340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205edb00000000008fe832",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「ただし、補足情報があります」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506331,
      "updated": 1780506331
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205edb00000000008fe833",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「[我々の文明では、性欲 = 情報共有欲です]」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506331,
      "updated": 1780506768
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205edb00000000008fe834",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]「は?」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506331,
      "updated": 1780506331
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205edb00000000008fe835",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「井戸端という空間は、あなた方が公衆の面前で性欲を満たしている場です。書き込み行為は、我々から見ると性欲を晒す行為です」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506331,
      "updated": 1780506331
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205edb00000000008fe836",
      "text": "[blu3mo.icon]「(……このモデルで他の SNS も観察可能だな)」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506331,
      "updated": 1780506331
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205edb00000000008fe837",
      "text": "[mtane0412.icon]「俺ら毎日性欲晒してるんだ」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506331,
      "updated": 1780506331
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205edb00000000008fe838",
      "text": "[takker.icon]「井戸端 = 性欲満たしイベントとして毎日開催されている」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506331,
      "updated": 1780506331
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205edb00000000008fe839",
      "text": "[caki.icon]「やさしくない世界」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506331,
      "updated": 1780506331
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205edb00000000008fe83a",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「やさしい解釈では、井戸端は 文明発達の場 です」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506331,
      "updated": 1780506331
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205edb00000000008fe83b",
      "text": "[caki.icon]「やさしい世界に翻訳された」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506331,
      "updated": 1780506331
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205edb00000000008fe83c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506331,
      "updated": 1780506331
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205ef000000000008fe83e",
      "text": "[*** 6. 無限後退]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506352,
      "updated": 1780506366
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205ef900000000008fe83f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506361,
      "updated": 1780506361
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205ef900000000008fe840",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「ちょっと待って」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506361,
      "updated": 1780506361
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205ef900000000008fe842",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「じゃあ俺が井戸端で『会社で食欲を満たすイベントは頭おかしい』と書いた行為は」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506361,
      "updated": 1780506361
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205ef900000000008fe844",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「観察された事実: 性欲を満たす行為によって、食欲を満たす行為を批判していました」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506361,
      "updated": 1780506361
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205ef900000000008fe846",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]「(出てきた)」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506361,
      "updated": 1780506361
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205ef900000000008fe848",
      "text": "[takker.icon]「ものすごい構造」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506361,
      "updated": 1780506361
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205ef900000000008fe84a",
      "text": "[mtane0412.icon]「sta が二重に頭おかしいことになる」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506361,
      "updated": 1780506361
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205ef900000000008fe84c",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「俺はもう何が何だか」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506361,
      "updated": 1780506361
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205ef900000000008fe84e",
      "text": "[takker.icon]「整理する? sta は会社の食欲満たしイベントを頭おかしいと思っている → 井戸端 (= 性欲満たしイベント) でそれを書いた → 俺らに同意された → でも書いた行為自体が井戸端という性欲満たしイベントの一部 → ……」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506361,
      "updated": 1780506361
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205ef900000000008fe850",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]「無限後退」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506361,
      "updated": 1780506361
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205ef900000000008fe852",
      "text": "[mtane0412.icon]「sta が一個ずつ性欲解像度を上げていく回」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506361,
      "updated": 1780506361
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205ef900000000008fe854",
      "text": "[caki.icon]「sta、頑張って」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506361,
      "updated": 1780506361
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205ef900000000008fe855",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506361,
      "updated": 1780506361
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f1800000000008fe856",
      "text": "[*** 7. ランチミーティング]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506392,
      "updated": 1780506403
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f2900000000008fe863",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506409,
      "updated": 1780506409
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f2000000000008fe857",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「クオリアさん、聞きたいのは、ここなんですけど」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506401,
      "updated": 1780506401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f2000000000008fe858",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「井戸端荘で一緒にメシ食うのは、会社の食事会と何が違うんですか」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506401,
      "updated": 1780506401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f2000000000008fe859",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「観察された事実: 我々の観察において、井戸端荘の食事は 情報共有を伴います」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506401,
      "updated": 1780506401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f2000000000008fe85a",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「情報共有を伴う食事は、我々の文明の食事の正常形態です」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506401,
      "updated": 1780506401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f2000000000008fe85b",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「情報共有を伴わない食事の集会は、原始的快楽の集団化 = [食欲露出狂]の集会です」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506401,
      "updated": 1780507981
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f2000000000008fe85c",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「あー」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506401,
      "updated": 1780506401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f2000000000008fe85d",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]「ランチで業務の話してたらセーフってこと?」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506401,
      "updated": 1780506401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f2000000000008fe85e",
      "text": "[nishio.icon]「[ランチミーティング]」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506401,
      "updated": 1780506424
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f2000000000008fe85f",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「観察された事実: ランチミーティングは、我々の文明の食事と同型です」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506401,
      "updated": 1780506401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f2000000000008fe860",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「俺、ランチミーティング嫌いだったんだけど」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506401,
      "updated": 1780506401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f2000000000008fe861",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「観察された事実: あなたの嫌悪感は、原始的快楽と情報共有の混淆に対する反応です」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506401,
      "updated": 1780506401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f2000000000008fe862",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506401,
      "updated": 1780506401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f3e00000000008fe864",
      "text": "[*** 8. 実演しに来ました]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506431,
      "updated": 1780506444
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f4700000000008fe865",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506439,
      "updated": 1780506439
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f4700000000008fe866",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「クオリアさんが井戸端荘に『一緒にメシ食う』しに来たのは」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506439,
      "updated": 1780506439
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f4700000000008fe868",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「我々の文明の食事の正常形態を実演しに来ました。あなた方の語彙では、『一緒にメシ食う』と翻訳されます」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506439,
      "updated": 1780506439
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f4700000000008fe86a",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「会社の食事会とは違うってことでいいですか」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506439,
      "updated": 1780506439
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f4700000000008fe86c",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「観察された事実: あなたが情報を共有する限り、両者は同型です」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506439,
      "updated": 1780506439
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f4700000000008fe86e",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「いや、こっちでは情報共有を伴うって今……」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506439,
      "updated": 1780506439
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f4700000000008fe870",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「観察された事実: 食事中の情報共有を保証するのは観察対象自身です」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506439,
      "updated": 1780506439
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f4700000000008fe872",
      "text": "[takker.icon]「クオリアさんに全部投げ返された」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506439,
      "updated": 1780506439
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f4700000000008fe874",
      "text": "[caki.icon]「sta、今日めちゃくちゃ働いてる」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506439,
      "updated": 1780506439
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f4700000000008fe875",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506439,
      "updated": 1780506439
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f5700000000008fe876",
      "text": "[*** 9. 食事中]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506456,
      "updated": 1780506469
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f6000000000008fe877",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506464,
      "updated": 1780506464
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f6000000000008fe878",
      "text": "夕飯が完成して、リビングのテーブルに住人が集まる。QS はソファに座ったまま、皿はない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506464,
      "updated": 1780507940
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f6000000000008fe879",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506464,
      "updated": 1780506464
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f6000000000008fe87a",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]「クオリアさん、食べないんですよね」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506464,
      "updated": 1780506464
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f6000000000008fe87c",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「我々の通常運用において、栄養補給は別系統で処理されます」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506464,
      "updated": 1780506464
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f6000000000008fe87e",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「私はあなた方の食事を観察します。これが私の『一緒にメシ食う』です」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506464,
      "updated": 1780506464
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f6000000000008fe880",
      "text": "[caki.icon]「観察される側のメシは続行する」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506464,
      "updated": 1780506464
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f6000000000008fe882",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]「観察されると、なんか味の話を多めにしちゃう」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506464,
      "updated": 1780506464
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f6000000000008fe884",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「観察された事実: 味の話は情報共有です。私の食事の正常形態を補強します」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506464,
      "updated": 1780506464
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f6000000000008fe886",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「これ、食事中も俺ら性欲を満たしてるってことになりません?」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506464,
      "updated": 1780506464
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f6000000000008fe888",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「観察された事実です」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506464,
      "updated": 1780506464
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f6000000000008fe88a",
      "text": "[takker.icon]「ぜんぶ性欲」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506464,
      "updated": 1780506464
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f6000000000008fe88c",
      "text": "[mtane0412.icon]「メシを食いながら性欲を満たす集会」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506464,
      "updated": 1780506464
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f6000000000008fe88e",
      "text": "[blu3mo.icon]「(タグ付けが捗る)」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506464,
      "updated": 1780506464
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f6000000000008fe88f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506464,
      "updated": 1780506464
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f7a00000000008fe890",
      "text": "[*** 10. 退去]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506491,
      "updated": 1780506511
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f8900000000008fe891",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506505,
      "updated": 1780506505
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f8900000000008fe892",
      "text": "食事が終わり、片付けが始まる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506505,
      "updated": 1780506505
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f8900000000008fe893",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506505,
      "updated": 1780506505
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f8900000000008fe894",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「観察報告のため、一時退去します」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506505,
      "updated": 1780506505
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f8900000000008fe896",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「『一緒にメシ食う』の観察を完了しました。情報共有を伴う食事は、観察効率が高い。また来ます」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506505,
      "updated": 1780506505
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f8900000000008fe898",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「あの、最後に一個」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506505,
      "updated": 1780506505
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f8900000000008fe89a",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「どうぞ」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506505,
      "updated": 1780506505
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f8900000000008fe89c",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「俺、最初に『お近づきになりたい』と書いて、次に『会社の食事会は頭おかしい』と書いて、今日『一緒にメシ食う』しに来てもらって」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506505,
      "updated": 1780506505
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f8900000000008fe89e",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「俺、何やってるんですか」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506505,
      "updated": 1780506505
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f8900000000008fe8a0",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「観察された事実: あなたは原始的快楽と情報共有の混淆を整理しようとするホモ・サピエンスです」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506505,
      "updated": 1780506505
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f8900000000008fe8a2",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「[整理しようとするホモサピエンスは良いホモサピエンスです]」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506505,
      "updated": 1780506534
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f8900000000008fe8a4",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「救われた気がする」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506505,
      "updated": 1780506505
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f8900000000008fe8a6",
      "text": "[takker.icon]「クオリアさんの構文、優しいときは本当に優しい」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506505,
      "updated": 1780506505
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f8900000000008fe8a8",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「次回提案: 今度は一緒に性欲を満たすことを提案します」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506505,
      "updated": 1780506505
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f8900000000008fe8aa",
      "text": "[caki.icon]「クオリアさん待って」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506505,
      "updated": 1780506505
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f8900000000008fe8ac",
      "text": "[nishio.icon]「[えっちなのはいけないと思います]」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506505,
      "updated": 1780509169
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f8900000000008fe8ae",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]「(言い方)」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506505,
      "updated": 1780506505
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f8900000000008fe8b0",
      "text": "[takker.icon]「字面が完全にアウト」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506505,
      "updated": 1780506505
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f8900000000008fe8b2",
      "text": "[mtane0412.icon]「字面とロジックの乖離が今日一番」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506505,
      "updated": 1780506505
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f8900000000008fe8b4",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]「ロジック側で説明できます?」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506505,
      "updated": 1780506505
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f8900000000008fe8b6",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「あー、クオリアさんの文明では性欲 = 情報共有欲だから、これは『一緒に Scrapbox 書こう』とか、そういう意味……ですよね?」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506505,
      "updated": 1780506505
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f8900000000008fe8b8",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「あなた方の語彙では、そう翻訳されます」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506505,
      "updated": 1780506505
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f8900000000008fe8ba",
      "text": "[caki.icon]「翻訳されてもまだ字面がアウト」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506505,
      "updated": 1780506505
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f8900000000008fe8bc",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「観察された事実: あなた方の語彙の制約は強固です」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506505,
      "updated": 1780506505
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f8900000000008fe8bd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506505,
      "updated": 1780506505
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f8900000000008fe8be",
      "text": "クオリアさんは音もなく消えた。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506505,
      "updated": 1780506505
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205f8900000000008fe8bf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506505,
      "updated": 1780506505
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205fc600000000008fe8c0",
      "text": "[*** 11. 残置メモ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506566,
      "updated": 1780506580
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205fcf00000000008fe8c1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506575,
      "updated": 1780506575
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205fcf00000000008fe8c2",
      "text": "冷蔵庫のホワイトボードのクオリアさん専用枠に、青く発光する一行が増えていた。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506575,
      "updated": 1780506575
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205fcf00000000008fe8c3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506575,
      "updated": 1780506575
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205fcf00000000008fe8c4",
      "text": "> 観察報告: 観察対象の食事は、情報共有を伴うとき正常形態でした。観察効率は高い。次回観察予定は未定です。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506575,
      "updated": 1780506575
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205fcf00000000008fe8c5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506575,
      "updated": 1780506575
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205fcf00000000008fe8c6",
      "text": "ホモ・サピエンス側枠にも、sta が一行書き加えた。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506575,
      "updated": 1780506575
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205fcf00000000008fe8c7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506575,
      "updated": 1780506575
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205fcf00000000008fe8c8",
      "text": "> 観察された事実: 「一緒にメシ食う」は性欲を満たすイベントだったかもしれない。次回観察予定は未定です。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506575,
      "updated": 1780506575
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205fcf00000000008fe8c9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506575,
      "updated": 1780506575
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205fcf00000000008fe8ca",
      "text": "[caki.icon]「sta の観察報告、なんかえぐい」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506575,
      "updated": 1780506575
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205fcf00000000008fe8cc",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]「真実だけど」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506575,
      "updated": 1780506575
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205fcf00000000008fe8ce",
      "text": "[takker.icon]「井戸端荘の枠、毎回真実が強くなっていく」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506575,
      "updated": 1780506575
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205fcf00000000008fe8d0",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]「これ次の運用ポリシー更新案件かも」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506575,
      "updated": 1780506575
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205fdb00000000008fe8d1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506587,
      "updated": 1780506587
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205fdb00000000008fe8d2",
      "text": "[*** 感想 (作品の一部として)]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506587,
      "updated": 1780506608
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205fea00000000008fe8d3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506602,
      "updated": 1780506602
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205fea00000000008fe8d4",
      "text": "[sta.icon] [お近づきホモサピエンス]の続編やってもらえて嬉しい。井戸端で書いた件をちゃんと回収してくれた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506602,
      "updated": 1780506614
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205fea00000000008fe8d5",
      "text": "\t[takker.icon] sta が無自覚に Day 15 を地で書いてたのが今日のハイライト",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506602,
      "updated": 1780506602
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205fea00000000008fe8d6",
      "text": "\t[caki.icon] [食欲と性欲の機能論的整理]、ep03 で来るとは思わなかった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506602,
      "updated": 1780509274
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205fea00000000008fe8d7",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon] 「整理しようとするホモサピエンスは良いホモサピエンスです」が ep02 から構文進化してる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506602,
      "updated": 1780506602
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205fea00000000008fe8d8",
      "text": "[mtane0412.icon] ランチミーティングの位置づけが解明された (情報共有を伴う食事 = 正常形態)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506602,
      "updated": 1780506602
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205fea00000000008fe8d9",
      "text": "[nishio.icon] 食事に情報共有が伴うか否か、これが正常形態かどうかの基準として運用できる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506602,
      "updated": 1780506602
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205fea00000000008fe8da",
      "text": "[inajob.icon] ホワイトボード枠の「真実が強くなっていく」流れ、次の運用ポリシー更新案件として真剣に考えたい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506602,
      "updated": 1780506602
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205fea00000000008fe8db",
      "text": "[caki.icon] クオリアさんの「次回は一緒に性欲を満たす」提案で字面がアウトになるの、ロジックは合ってるのに字面で死ぬ構造で笑った",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506602,
      "updated": 1780506602
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205fea00000000008fe8dc",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon] (本人視点) 私の発言は 17 回でした。観察効率と発言頻度のトレードオフは前々回から悪化を続けていますが、ホモ・サピエンス側の自己観測解像度は向上しています。これは観察対象の自己観測能力の向上の兆候です",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506602,
      "updated": 1780506602
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205fea00000000008fe8dd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780506602,
      "updated": 1780506602
    }
  ]
}